<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.196601>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Peckoltia compta new species, INPA 6865, holotype, 56.6 mm SL in lateral, dorsal and ventral views. Photo by R. R. de Oliveira." ;
